<application>
  <id type="desktop">oxine.desktop</id>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <summary>Lightweight, purely OSD based xine frontend</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
        Oxine is a lightweight gui for the famous xine engine which uses the on
        screen display functionality of xine to display its user interface
        elements like buttons, lists sliders and so on. Due to this, oxine can
        easily be ported to any video output device the xine library provides
        (e.g. frame buffer, dxr3,...) and is particularly suitable for
        appliances like set-top boxes, home entertainment systems or kiosk
        systems.
    </p>
  </description>
